items.headline: Welcome to the Tenchi Muyo Wiki!
items.desc:
Welcome to the Tenchi Muyo! Wiki (a.k.a. Tenchipedia) This wiki is a resource for Tenchi Muyo fans to share their knowledge of the series.

Tenchi Muyo! is a Japanese anime, light novel, and manga series created by Masaki Kajishima and Hiroki Hayashi. We encourage new users on the wiki to contribute and edit as much as they can!
